news.headline: UnitedHealth stock ticks lower amid expanded Justice Department probe
news.summary: Investing.com -- Unitedhealth Group (NYSE:UNH) stock fell 1.4% in late Tuesday trade following reports that the U.S. Justice Department’s criminal investigation into the health insurance giant has expanded beyond previously known Medicare fraud inquiries.
